webpackJsonp([20218861871774],{1059:function(t,e){t.exports={data:{wordpressPost:{title:"Breathe Better To Reduce Stress and Boost Your Complexion",content:'<p>You’re a grownup so you likely already know a lot about skin care. You’re aware you need to follow a reasonably dedicated regime if you want your <strong>complexion to really look its best</strong>.</p>\n<p>And you know that means thorough cleansing both morning and night, a serum targeted to treat your skin concerns, eye cream, a moisturiser with a high level SPF during the day plus a moisturiser rich with antioxidants and other powerful active ingredients at night time.</p>\n<p>Did you know though that <strong>even the best of skincare habits won’t make your skin glow</strong> if you don’t have your stress levels under control? Unfortunately that’s the truth. Hopefully this little nugget didn’t make you feel more stressed! If it did, take a deep breath and let the worry go.</p>\n<figure id="attachment_2003" style="width: 239px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-medium wp-image-2003" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/16232700/yoga-jpg-239x300.jpg" alt="" width="239" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/16232700/yoga-jpg-239x300.jpg 239w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/16232700/yoga-jpg.jpg 475w" sizes="(max-width: 239px) 100vw, 239px" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Image: Instagram/@amandabisk</figcaption></figure>\n<p>The fact of the matter is while <strong>you can’t completely remove stress, you can reduce it dramatically</strong> and all it takes is a few simple streps.</p>\n<p>Taking a few minutes each morning and each night to introduce a mindfulness practise is a brilliant way to ease the pressure. If you’re not doing that already get started by doing the following.</p>\n<figure id="attachment_2004" style="width: 243px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-medium wp-image-2004" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/16232824/Amanda-jpg-243x300.jpg" alt="" width="243" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/16232824/Amanda-jpg-243x300.jpg 243w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/16232824/Amanda-jpg.jpg 475w" sizes="(max-width: 243px) 100vw, 243px" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Image: Instagram/@amandabisk</figcaption></figure>\n<p>Focus on your breathing for a moment. Then, inhale to the count of four, hold to the count of four, then exhale to the count of four. Repeat the process adding a second to each exhalation until you reach a count of eight. Continue for at least five minutes.</p>\n<p><strong>Did you try it already?</strong> If yes, you no doubt feel better. If not, do it when you can. Your body will thank you for it and you know what that means? Dewier, more relaxed, lovely-looking skin.</p>\n<p>For more inspirational lifestyle tips and also pictures follow <a href="https://www.instagram.com/amandabisk/">Amanda Bisk here.</a> The former gymnast and professional pole vaulter is now a fully qualified yoga teacher and all-round amazing woman. Props to you Amanda.</p>\n',better_featured_image:{source_url:"http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/09203709/PP-.jpg"},categories:[{slug:"lifestyle",name:"Lifestyle"},{slug:"skincare",name:"Skincare"}]},site:{siteMetadata:{title:"The Beauty Insider"}}},pathContext:{id:"49fe2cdf-351e-5406-b0ed-f7fee5641e60"}}}});
//# sourceMappingURL=path---simple-trick-will-instantly-improve-skin-bdc2e286c3207501d904.js.map